In Ableton Live you can add song markers or as their called in Live, song ''locators''.

To do this first find the place you would like to add a song locator.

Then right click in the upper space between the grid display and the top of the first track.

[[File:Ableton Live add locator.png]]


Then you can name the locator in the space that appears.


[[File:Ableton Live nameing marker.png]]


You can also right click the marker flag for additional parameters such as delete, renaming etc.


[[File:Ableton Live right click marker flag.png]]


